/// @summary Selects built-in, system-following, or validated custom GUI themes.
/// @details
/// `Zanna.GUI.Theme` is an app-scoped static surface. Dark and Light are deterministic; System
/// follows the host appearance; Custom deep-copies a validated logical `ThemePalette`. Installed
